## ðŸ“ˆ Key Features & Steps

### ðŸ”¹ Data Cleaning
- Renamed and structured columns 
- Changed data types for clear visualization
- Unpivoted monthly data for flexible analysis
- Created derived columns for calendar dates

### ðŸ”¹ Data Modeling
- Built relationships using common columns (e.g., date keys, salesperson/team)

### ðŸ”¹ DAX Calculations
- `Total Sales Actual`, `Total Sales Target`, `Variance`, `Variance %`
- Year-to-Date (YTD), Month-to-Date (MTD), and dynamic formatting of chart title
